08, properties:{quote:"all of the partnerships, which enron used to finance projects in a way that kept them off the balance sheet, have become the once-proud company's bane. the sec is investigating potential conflict-of-interest issues involving two such partnerships on which ousted chief financial officer andrew fastow served as general partner."}}, {_id:1111, properties:{quote:"it also warned that a further drop in its credit rating could force it to pay $3.9 billion to other partnerships, the bulk of it to osprey trust and marlin water trust."}}, {_id:1116, properties:{quote:"enron said its cash friday had fallen to $1.2-bil, even with the dynegy payment three days earlier, $550-mil drawn on a new bank line last week and $3-bil drawn on existing lines earlier this month to pay off $1.9-bil of commercial paper."}}, {_id:1119, properties:{quote:"from: \tpolsky, phil  sent:\ttuesday, november 20, 2001 8:32 am to:\tward, kim s (houston) subject:\tenron wire articles"}}, {_id:1121, properties:{quote:"to:\tward, kim s (houston)"}}] AS row
